<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Management System Activation Email</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
      /* Base Styles */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #FAFAFA;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      /* Header */
      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      /* Content Body */
      .email-body {
        padding: 40px 30px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      /* Activation Code Box */
      .activation-code-box {
        background-color: #f0f7ff;
        border: 2px dashed #0070f3;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .activation-code-box h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        color: #0070f3;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      }
      /* Footer */
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777777;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #0070f3;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to MS</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="email-body">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0;">Hello <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with <strong>ELearning</strong>. To activate your account and start your learning journey, please use the following activation code:</p>
        
        <div class="activation-code-box">
          <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">
          Please enter this code on the activation page within the next <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
        </p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #999999;">
          If you did not register for an ELearning account, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:mirajhossen.cse@gmail.com">mirajhossen.cse@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p>&copy; 2026 ELearning Platform</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>